config GPIO_SIM
    bool "GPIO emulator with external drive simulation"
    depends on GPIO
    default y if DT_HAS_QUICKRECON_GPIO_SIM_ENABLED
    help
      GPIO emulator that tracks externally-driven pins. Pins set via
      gpio_sim_drive() preserve their value through pull-up/pull-down
      reconfigurations, simulating real pin capacitance behavior.
